{"tid":852431,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"火車又delay 有人跳軌","createTime":"2018-10-08T00:22:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T00:39:52.000Z","uid":33333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b309dbf2e80c6fabaecf05f8b738924138739e2a","tid":852431,"uid":33333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T00:22:53.000Z","msg":"早上8時許，港鐵東鐵綫粉嶺站2號月台有人墮軌，太和站來回上水站服務暫停，救援人員正趕往現場拯救。<br />\n<br />\n受意外影響，紅磡站來回大埔墟站6分鐘一班車；紅磡站來回太和站10分鐘一班車。上水站來回羅湖站10分鐘一班車，上水站來回落馬洲站15分鐘一班車。港鐵表示地正安排免費接駁巴士，行走太和站至上水站，呼籲乘客為行程預留充裕時間。"},{"pid":"c04c248961aba6e8eec89677703beb60e2c20ebf","tid":852431,"uid":109268,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T00:28:30.000Z","msg":"點解要揀返工返學時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25c83723a85885305acc1587d00c8486260e1de2","tid":852431,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T00:29:13.000Z","msg":"生又累人 死又累街坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2ef0d3232b8e010e2622a31f7c9c763a33cfc45","tid":852431,"uid":85427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T00:29:25.000Z","msg":"本來去緊粉嶺㗎車回咗頭 放哂d人岀去 接去紅磡嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae79a6e92bec1608806ab73a30772122d7e0e8a8","tid":852431,"uid":93951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T00:29:35.000Z","msg":"係上水一入閘就見到架火車開門停左係到都知瀨野手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後先廣播話粉嶺有人誤墜<br />\n叫乘客轉乘其他交通工具<br />\n出到閘巴士條龍已經長到on9 <br />\n唉"},{"pid":"2b7a4bd1d008132e3044571fad98786a5e1fb5fa","tid":852431,"uid":95418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T00:31:44.000Z","msg":"又要遲到了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"240287d0118fea5415436e0c4466c2135c7169c8","tid":852431,"uid":33333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T00:34:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee8743d99304bd4cc3f154eddee63cc5db62a0d2","tid":852431,"uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T00:37:21.000Z","msg":"一鳩車撚死佢咪算 有勇氣死不如去斬死啲仆街啦<br />\n<br />\n例如啲煙產火車頭 政治賣港賊 乜撚都好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe65556cd59f60080e3689bf64ab2fd5bc30fa8","tid":852431,"uid":33333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T00:39:52.000Z","msg":"慘 我架車唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}